; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;图一</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-top: 16px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;出现此问题是在安装软件的时候软件版本号未写入到注册表中，解决此问题的步骤具体如下：</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-top: 16px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;1、在键盘中键入win+R组合键，在文本框中输入“regedit”然后回车</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-top: 16px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2、依次打开文件夹：“HKEY_CURRENT_USER—&gt;Software”找到“ABRITES”文件夹并点击该文件夹，并在右侧框中新建Version=14,新建方法如下：</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-top: 16px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ①在右侧框中点击鼠标右键，选择&quot;新建&quot;—&gt;选择&quot;DWORD(32位)值(D)&quot;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-top: 16px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ②正确执行①中的步骤时会在右侧框中新增一个选项，鼠标右击该选项选择&quot;重命名(R)&quot;输入&quot;Version&quot;(不要把双引号也输入进去)回车</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-top: 16px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ③鼠标双击&quot;Version&quot;在&quot;数值数据(V)&quot;下方输入&quot;14&quot;后点击确定即可。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-top: 16px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;3、依次打开文件夹：<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">“</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE—&gt;SOFTWARE-&gt;Wow6432Node</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">”(64位电脑)</span>或者&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">“</span>HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE-&gt;SOFTWARE<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">”(32位电脑)找到<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">“ABRITES”文件夹并点击该文件夹，并在右侧框中新建Version=14,新建方法同上。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-top: 16px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;4、退出重新在OBD终结者软件中打开丰田软件基本上不会出现同样的问题，请按照步骤仔细操作。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-top: 16px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-top: 16px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 以上是解决ABRITS Version报错问题的具体步骤，详情文档请下载&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.baidu.com/\" target=\"_self\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(75, 182, 245);\">ABRUTES版本问题解决方案.docx</a>&nbsp;如若解决步骤繁琐，请下载<a href=\"http://www.baidu.com/\" target=\"_self\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(75, 182, 245);\">ABRUTES_Version_14.reg</a>到电脑双击该文件即可（备注：在下载ABRUTES_Version_14.reg文件时需要退出杀毒软件，不然会被杀毒软件隔离导致下载失败。）</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-top: 16px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-top: 16px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-top: 16px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0