m: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-top: 16px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;4、退出重新在OBD终结者软件中打开丰田软件基本上不会出现同样的问题，请按照步骤仔细操作。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-top: 16px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-top: 16px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 以上是解决ABRITS Version报错问题的具体步骤，详情文档请下载&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.baidu.com/\" target=\"_self\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(75, 182, 245);\">ABRUTES版本问题解决方案.docx</a>&nbsp;如若解决步骤繁琐，请下载<a href=\"http://www.baidu.com/\" target=\"_self\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(75, 182, 245);\">ABRUTES_Version_14.reg</a>到电脑双击该文件即可（备注：在下载ABRUTES_Version_14.reg文件时需要退出杀毒软件，不然会被杀毒软件隔离导致下载失败。）</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-top: 16px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-top: 16px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-top: 16px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 如有任何疑问请联系王工QQ:3004430581</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','OBD终结者打开丰田软件报ABRITES Version错误解决方案','','inherit','closed','closed','','91-revision-v1','','','2017-12-09 10:36:42','2017-12-09 02:36:42','',91,'http://47.52.160.15/index.php/2017/12/09/91-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(95,1,'2017-12-09 10:37:47','2017-12-09 02:37:47','<p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; 当用户打开TM100钥匙编程器的时候，会提示TM100连接错误提示，如下图所示：</p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img title=\"1511339194116573.png\" alt=\"Tm100.png\" src=\"http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/image/20171122/1511339194116573.png\"/>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; 图一</p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;弹出该提示框主要是因为连接设备的驱动未更新导致或者COM端口驱动编号大于10，我们需要更新两个驱动或者将端口驱动COM编号改成10以下。</p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(28, 28, 28); padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">TM100解决连接错误操作步骤如下</strong></span>：</p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;1、连接好设备，打开TM100确定是不是TM100连接错误，如上图一</p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;2、如果是连接错误问题在电脑桌面上找到&quot;我的电脑&quot;右击&quot;我的电脑&quot;—&gt;选择&quot;管理&quot;—&gt;选择&quot;设备管理器&quot;（系统工具下方最后一个）并双击，在右侧框框中找到&quot;USB Serial Port(COM<span style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: #FF0000; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">X</span>)&quot;和&quot;USB Serial Converter&quot;这两个驱动（X-是一个编号，这个编号不能大于10）如下图：</p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;<img title=\"1511340890899192.png\" alt=\"TM100_01.png\" src=\"http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/image/20171122/1511340890899192.png\"/><img title=\"1511340907893597.png\" alt=\"TM100_02.png\" src=\"http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/image/20171122/1511340907893597.png\"/></p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;3、分别更新这两个驱动，这两个驱动更新方式是一样的，这里以更新&quot;USB Serial Port(COM6)&quot;驱动为例</p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ①下载<a style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(75, 182, 245); padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"http://www.baidu.com/\" target=\"_self\">TM100驱动</a>(点击此处下载)并解压，记住驱动解压位置。</p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ②右击&quot;<span style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: #FF0000; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">USB Serial Port(COM6)</span>&quot;—&gt;选择&quot;<span style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: #FF0000; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">更新驱动程序软件</span>&quot;—&gt;选择&quot;<span style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: #FF0000; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">浏览计算机以查找驱动程序软件（R）</span>&quot;（第二个选项）—&gt;选择&quot;<span style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: #FF0000; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">从计算机的设备驱动程序列表中选取（L）</span>&quot;(选第二个选项)—&gt;选择&quot;<span style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: #FF0000; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">从磁盘安装</span>&quot;—&gt;选中USB Serial Port后选择&quot;<span style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: #FF0000; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">浏览</span>&quot;找到刚刚解压TM100驱动文件下的&quot;<span style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: #FF0000; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">ftdiport.inf</span>&quot;这个文件<strong style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(28, 28, 28); padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">（更新USB Serial Converter驱动的时候选择&quot;ftdibus.inf&quot;这个文件）</strong>文件位置一般在&quot;…PID0000\\PID0000Driver\\CDM v2.10.00 WHQL Certified PID0000&quot;文件夹下方。</p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ③选中文件后点击确定—&gt;下一步—&gt;关闭即可。更新<strong style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(28, 28, 28); padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline;\">USB Serial Converter驱动操作同上。</strong></p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\"><strong style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(28, 28, 28); padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><br/></strong></p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\"><strong style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(28, 28, 28); padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">设置USB Serial Port(COM<span style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: #FF0000; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">X</span>)&nbsp;<span style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: #FF0000; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">X</span>小于10的操作步骤：</strong></strong></p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\"><strong style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(28, 28, 28); padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></strong>&nbsp;①选择USB Serial Port(COMx)右击属性</p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;②在弹框的上方选择&quot;端口设置&quot;后再下方选择&quot;高级设置&quot;</p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;③在弹框最顶上的&quot;COM端口号（P）&quot;右侧选择可用的并且小于10的端口号。</p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;④选择好端口号后在右侧点击确定，后面一直点击确定即可。</p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;<img title=\"1511343414687389.png\" alt=\"TM100_03.png\" src=\"http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/image/20171122/1511343414687389.png\"/></p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\"><strong style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(28, 28, 28); padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline;\">连接设备后未找到&quot;USB Serial Port(COM)&quot;和&quot;USB Serial Converter&quot;驱动解决方案</strong></p><p 