;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(28, 28, 28);\"><br/></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-top: 16px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(28, 28, 28);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">设置USB Serial Port(COM<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #FF0000;\">X</span>)&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #FF0000;\">X</span>小于10的操作步骤：</strong></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-top: 16px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(28, 28, 28);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></strong>&nbsp;①选择USB Serial Port(COMx)右击属性</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-top: 16px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;②在弹框的上方选择&quot;端口设置&quot;后再下方选择&quot;高级设置&quot;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-top: 16px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;③在弹框最顶上的&quot;COM端口号（P）&quot;右侧选择可用的并且小于10的端口号。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-top: 16px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;④选择好端口号后在右侧点击确定，后面一直点击确定即可。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-top: 16px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;<img src=\"http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/image/20171122/1511343414687389.png\" title=\"1511343414687389.png\" alt=\"TM100_03.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-top: 16px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-top: 16px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(28, 28, 28);\">连接设备后未找到&quot;USB Serial Port(COM)&quot;和&quot;USB Serial Converter&quot;驱动解决方案</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-top: 16px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; 出现这种情况有三种情况</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-top: 16px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; 1、第一种情况是TM100的USB线出了问题，更换或者重新拔插一下即可</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-top: 16px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; 2、第二种情是电脑问题，更换电脑即可。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-top: 16px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; 2、第二种情况方案是未成功安装驱动，有USB Serial Port(COM)&quot;和&quot;USB Serial Converter驱动显示但带有感叹号，需要安装驱动（此处安装驱动跟上面安装驱动不一样）</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-top: 16px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;此处安装驱动方式：下载TM100驱动并解压，右击“USB Serial Port(COM)”选择&quot;更新驱动程序软件&quot;—&gt;选择&quot;浏览计算机以查找驱动程序软件&quot;—&gt;选择&quot;浏览&quot;找到解压后的文件夹即可。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-top: 16px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;（<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">USB Serial Converter驱动带有感叹号安装驱动与<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">USB Serial Port(COM)带有感叹号需要安装驱动步骤一样</span></span>）</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-top: 16px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-top: 16px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-top: 16px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">备注：如有疑问请在联系我们中找到我们的联系方式即可。</p><p><br/></p>','TM100连接错误“解决方案','',