ed','','31-revision-v1','','','2017-12-11 10:38:04','2017-12-11 02:38:04','',31,'http://47.52.160.15/index.php/2017/12/11/31-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(109,1,'2017-12-11 12:25:34','2017-12-11 04:25:34','','5040311921_f20b3122e0_b','','inherit','open','closed','','5040311921_f20b3122e0_b','','','2017-12-11 12:25:34','2017-12-11 04:25:34','',95,'http://47.52.160.15/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/5040311921_f20b3122e0_b.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(110,1,'2017-12-11 12:26:00','2017-12-11 04:26:00','<p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; 当用户打开TM100钥匙编程器的时候，会提示TM100连接错误提示，如下图所示：</p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img title=\"1511339194116573.png\" alt=\"Tm100.png\" src=\"http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/image/20171122/1511339194116573.png\"/>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; 图一</p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;弹出该提示框主要是因为连接设备的驱动未更新导致或者COM端口驱动编号大于10，我们需要更新两个驱动或者将端口驱动COM编号改成10以下。</p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(28, 28, 28); padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">TM100解决连接错误操作步骤如下</strong></span>：</p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;1、连接好设备，打开TM100确定是不是TM100连接错误，如上图一</p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;2、如果是连接错误问题在电脑桌面上找到&quot;我的电脑&quot;右击&quot;我的电脑&quot;—&gt;选择&quot;管理&quot;—&gt;选择&quot;设备管理器&quot;（系统工具下方最后一个）并双击，在右侧框框中找到&quot;USB Serial Port(COM<span style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: #FF0000; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">X</span>)&quot;和&quot;USB Serial Converter&quot;这两个驱动（X-是一个编号，这个编号不能大于10）如下图：</p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;<img title=\"1511340890899192.png\" alt=\"TM100_01.png\" src=\"http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/image/20171122/1511340890899192.png\"/><img title=\"1511340907893597.png\" alt=\"TM100_02.png\" src=\"http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/image/20171122/1511340907893597.png\"/></p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;3、分别更新这两个驱动，这两个驱动更新方式是一样的，这里以更新&quot;USB Serial Port(COM6)&quot;驱动为例</p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ①下载<a style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(75, 182, 245); padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"http://www.baidu.com/\" target=\"_self\">TM100驱动</a>(点击此处下载)并解压，记住驱动解压位置。</p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ②右击&quot;<span style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: #FF0000; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">USB Serial Port(COM6)</span>&quot;—&gt;选择&quot;<span style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: #FF0000; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">更新驱动程序软件</span>&quot;—&gt;选择&quot;<span style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: #FF0000; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">浏览计算机以查找驱动程序软件（R）</span>&quot;（第二个选项）—&gt;选择&quot;<span style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: #FF0000; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">从计算机的设备驱动程序列表中选取（L）</span>&quot;(选第二个选项)—&gt;选择&quot;<span style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: #FF0000; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">从磁盘安装</span>&quot;—&gt;选中USB Serial Port后选择&quot;<span style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: #FF0000; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">浏览</span>&quot;找到刚刚解压TM100驱动文件下的&quot;<span style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: #FF0000; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">ftdiport.inf</span>&quot;这个文件<strong style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(28, 28, 28); padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">（更新USB Serial Converter驱动的时候选择&quot;ftdibus.inf&quot;这个文件）</strong>文件位置一般在&quot;…PID0000\\PID0000Driver\\CDM v2.10.00 WHQL Certified PID0000&quot;文件夹下方。</p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ③选中文件后点击确定—&gt;下一步—&gt;关闭即可。更新<strong style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(28, 28, 28); padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline;\">USB Serial Converter驱动操作同上。</strong></p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\"><strong style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(28, 28, 28); padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><br/></strong></p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\"><strong style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(28, 28, 28); padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">设置USB Serial Port(COM<span style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: #FF0000; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">X</span>)&nbsp;<span style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: #FF0000; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">X</span>小于10的操作步骤：</strong></strong></p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\"><strong style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(28, 28, 28); padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></strong>&nbsp;①选择USB Serial Port(COMx)右击属性</p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;②在弹框的上方选择&quot;端口设置&quot;后再下方选择&quot;高级设置&quot;</p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;③在弹框最顶上的&quot;COM端口号（P）&quot;右侧选择可用的并且小于10的端口号。</p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;④选择好端口号后在右侧点击确定，后面一直点击确定即可。</p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;<img title=\"1511343414687389.png\" alt=\"TM100_03.png\" src=\"http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/image/20171122/1511343414687389.png\"/></p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\"><strong style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(28, 28, 28); padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline;\">连接设备后未找到&quot;USB Serial Port(COM)&quot;和&quot;USB Serial Converter&quot;驱动解决方案</strong></p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; 出现这种情况有三种情况</p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; 1、第一种情况是TM100的USB线出了问题，更换或者重新拔插一下即可</p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; 2、第二种情是电脑问题，更换电脑即可。</p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; 2、第二种情况方案是未成功安装驱动，有USB Serial Port(COM)&quot;和&quot;USB Serial Converter驱动显示但带有感叹号，需要安装驱动（此处安装驱动跟上面安装驱动不一样）</p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;此处安装驱动方式：下载TM100驱动并解压，右击“USB Serial Port(COM)”选择&quot;更新驱动程序软件&quot;—&gt;选择&quot;浏览计算机以查找驱动程序软件&quot;—&gt;选择&quot;浏览&quot;找到解压后的文件夹即可。</p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;（<span style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline;\">USB Serial Converter驱动带有感叹号安装驱动与<span style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">USB Serial Port(COM)带有感叹号需要安装驱动步骤一样</span></span>）</p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(135, 135, 135); line-height: 26px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\">备注：如有疑问请在联系我们中找到我们的联系方式即可。</p><p><br/></p>','TM100连接错误“解决方案','','inherit','closed','closed','','95-revision-v1','','','2017-12-11 12:26:00','2017-12-11 04:26:00','',